=The Ascent of Ling Yun=

00:00:11.059 --> 00:00:13.312
=Episode 11=

00:00:13.491 --> 00:00:15.616
(I'll Discipline This Maid for You)

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:24.376
Consort Jing.

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:25.496
What do you think?

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.240
I am no expert to speak

00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:31.352
about the pill.

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:32.840
Please summon

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:35.000
imperial physicians
for a proper examination.

00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:37.520
Consort Jing, speak your mind.

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:42.000
Your Majesty,

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:44.560
this pill appears to be

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:47.040
a forbidden pill.

00:00:50.040 --> 00:00:51.128
Forbidden pill?

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:53.840
I only seek to replenish vital energy.

00:00:54.440 --> 00:00:55.600
Isn't it a tonic pill?

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.280
I have no idea, Your Highness.

00:00:57.560 --> 00:00:59.320
I only knew you were seeking this,

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:00.800
so I presented it to you.

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:01.880
How dare you!

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:03.840
When did I seek a forbidden pill?

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.160
How dare you slander me?

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:06.000
I wouldn't dare.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.280
I wouldn't, Your Highness.

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:08.680
It's Ling Yun's pill,

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:09.720
not mine.

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:11.960
She intended to curry favor with it.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:13.600
I wanted to be freed,

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:15.160
so I stole it from her

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:16.680
to present to you.

00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:18.520
I'd never frame you, Your Highness.

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:20.160
(It's Ling Yun again.)

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.680
Guards.

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:22.680
Summon Ling Yun.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:23.992
Yes.

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:31.160
May Your Majesty

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.320
be well.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:33.720
May Your Highnesses be well.

00:01:33.880 --> 00:01:34.840
Rise.

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:38.880
This maid presented this pill.

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.680
Did it come from you?

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:42.072
Your Majesty,

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:44.200
I know nothing of this pill.

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:45.880
What I do know

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:47.160
is that Cui Wei

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.520
colluded with Madam Sun
to exploit the Fragrance Bureau.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.640
I exposed Madam Sun's corruption.

00:01:52.760 --> 00:01:54.680
Cui Wei was demoted
to the Servitude Bureau.

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:55.920
She has harbored

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.440
resentment toward me

00:01:57.520 --> 00:01:58.440
and sought revenge.

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.320
Ling Yun.

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.880
How dare you lie to His Majesty?

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:04.160
You said Consort Wan sought this pill.

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:06.120
You prepared this as a gift

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.280
to seek her favor.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.760
Seek her favor?

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.160
How absurd.

00:02:10.920 --> 00:02:12.920
What was Consort Wan seeking?

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:14.080
This forbidden pill.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:17.400
Cui Wei.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:19.000
How could the well-respected

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.480
Consort Wan break palace rules?

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:23.080
Framing me is one thing.

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.280
But how dare you

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.520
slander Her Highness?

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:27.920
I'm wronged.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:29.440
I've always been

00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:30.360
loyal to you.

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:32.280
I never intended
to slander Your Highness.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.176
How dare you

00:02:33.176 --> 00:02:34.120
frame your fellow

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:35.040
and set me up?

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:36.000
You shall be punished.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.144
Chief Wu.

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:39.480
Will you let this wretch slander me?

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.760
Calm down, Your Highness.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.080
She deserves to die if she has

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:43.640
slandered you.

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:45.280
His Majesty will punish her.

00:02:49.848 --> 00:02:50.800
Your Majesty!

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:53.280
Your Majesty, I have something to say.

00:02:53.688 --> 00:02:54.680
Consort Wan...

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.240
Consort Wan sent Eunuch Shun Xi

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:58.840
to make me kill Ling Yun.

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:00.840
She promised to free me

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:02.560
from the Servitude Bureau.

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.280
But Ru Yi found out

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:06.280
before I could administer poison.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.000
Consort Wan

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:10.080
then asked me to kill Ru Yi.

00:03:10.320 --> 00:03:12.320
I confess to all those crimes.

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:15.680
But I have nothing to do
with the forbidden pill.

00:03:16.040 --> 00:03:17.080
Spare me, Your Majesty.

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.680
I was coerced.

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.960
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:22.560
This maid spews lies, Your Majesty.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.920
I've never met her privately,

00:03:25.160 --> 00:03:26.080
let alone

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:27.080
commissioned murder.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.520
Please discern the truth.

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:31.680
Your Majesty.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:32.800
As an imperial consort,

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:35.360
why would I mingle
with such a lowly maid?

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:36.448
I am innocent.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:39.440
The maids and servants

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:41.720
may be of humble status,

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:43.800
but all lives matter the same.

00:03:44.448 --> 00:03:45.320
Abuse and killing

00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:46.840
of the servants are forbidden.

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.080
How dare you

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:49.680
treat human lives as mere weeds

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:50.560
before His Majesty?

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:51.760
Your Majesty.

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:53.280
This wretched maid is slandering me.

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:54.440
When one scheme fails,

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:55.320
she hatches another.

00:03:55.880 --> 00:03:56.720
If there's evidence,

00:03:57.160 --> 00:03:58.920
I'll accept any punishment.

00:03:59.320 --> 00:04:01.480
I beg Your Majesty to clear my name.

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:03.320
I beg your judgment.

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:04.608
Your Majesty,

00:04:04.800 --> 00:04:06.880
Cui Wei has identified the mastermind.

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.224
Please

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:10.720
deliver justice for the slain maid.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.184
Your Majesty,

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:15.280
I recall something now.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.880
Some days ago,

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:19.960
Consort Wan took her servants
to the Servitude Bureau,

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:22.640
threatening to cut out
Ling Yun's tongue.

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:24.280
It appears to me

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.480
that Consort Wan harbors genuine hatred

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.840
toward this maid.

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:29.024
Consort Jing.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:30.480
What are you implying?

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.456
Enough.

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.320
Consort Wan,

00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:35.000
I granted you managerial authority

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:36.576
out of trust.

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:38.200
You should discipline

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:39.840
these maids and servants.

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.560
I leave this matter in your hands.

00:04:44.224 --> 00:04:45.216
Yes.

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:46.240
Thank you.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:48.880
I'll discipline these unruly servants.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.520
This young maid

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:54.000
has a cunning mind

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:55.168
and a sharp tongue.

00:04:55.640 --> 00:04:56.640
Send this troublemaker

00:04:57.200 --> 00:04:58.720
to the Imperial Study.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:02.208
I'll discipline her in person.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.600
We bid farewell to Your Majesty.

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:19.776
Ling Yun.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.280
I must admit

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:22.960
that you're quite something.

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:24.800
I never expected

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:27.120
that you'd be the first to leave here.

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:29.560
Cui Wei.

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:31.160
A few days ago,

00:05:31.640 --> 00:05:33.560
I wished you well in the next life.

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:35.600
Stop wagging your tongue

00:05:36.360 --> 00:05:38.040
- and prepare your funeral.
- You...

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:40.160
Mind your own business.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:43.240
You think you'll be safe
at the Imperial Study?

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.800
Serving His Majesty

00:05:45.523 --> 00:05:46.515
is like riding a tiger.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.216
Cui Wei.

00:05:53.760 --> 00:05:55.320
Ru Yi was my friend.

00:05:55.960 --> 00:05:57.160
You killed her.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.360
Do you think I'll let you off?

00:06:00.288 --> 00:06:01.360
An eye for an eye.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:02.240
A life for a life.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:03.080
That's justice.

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:04.840
I've warned you.

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:06.960
If I delivered that pill,

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:08.360
I could be released.

00:06:08.760 --> 00:06:09.728
But if you did it,

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.480
it would cost your life.

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.760
Did you think I was joking?

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:16.120
You knew all along

00:06:16.760 --> 00:06:18.400
that I killed Ru Yi.

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:20.736
Ru Yi.

00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:22.160
Ru Yi.

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:26.120
How tragic.

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:47.360
Eunuch Shun Xi.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:51.560
Here is all my savings.

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:53.760
I'll be at your service from now on.

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:55.600
Please plead for mercy

00:06:55.760 --> 00:06:56.800
before Her Highness.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:57.760
I swear.

00:06:57.960 --> 00:06:59.120
My life belongs

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:00.720
to you from now on.

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.760
Whatever you ask me to do,

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.200
I will obey

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:05.792
without hesitation.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:10.240
Cui Wei.

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:11.920
Your life

00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:13.400
belongs to Consort Wan.

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:15.200
I dare not claim it.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:16.704
Well,

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.160
Her Highness assigned me

00:07:18.640 --> 00:07:20.200
to bring you the favor.

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:29.520
See?

00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:31.880
This is the end.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.088
Your Majesty.

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:50.560
I have committed a crime.

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:52.240
(Imperial Study)
What crime?

00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:54.120
I deceived Your Majesty.

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:55.360
I'm detestable.

00:07:56.083 --> 00:07:56.960
(Imperial Study)

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:58.280
At least, you are aware

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:00.240
that you're detestable.

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:02.040
I obtained

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:02.960
that forbidden pill

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:05.160
from Consort Wan's palace.

00:08:05.760 --> 00:08:06.720
Consort Wan

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:09.760
realized that I had found out
about her scheme of seeking favor

00:08:09.760 --> 00:08:10.760
with the forbidden pill.

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:13.040
That's why she tried every means

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:15.640
to have me killed.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:17.200
I am aware of her scheme

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:18.400
of seeking favor.

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:21.240
But how dare you lure that maid

00:08:21.640 --> 00:08:23.000
into exposing the scandal

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.520
and causing disturbance?

00:08:25.080 --> 00:08:26.960
You've got some nerve.

00:08:27.760 --> 00:08:28.840
You are truly wise.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:30.280
So Your Majesty

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:32.880
knew about Consort Wan's
involvement with the forbidden pills

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:34.280
as well as

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:36.760
the tricks I employed.

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:39.488
Concubine Zhao's

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:41.040
dance shoes concealed a blade.

00:08:41.560 --> 00:08:42.560
You nearly died

00:08:42.560 --> 00:08:43.640
from meddling with it.

00:08:44.160 --> 00:08:45.320
I spared you

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:46.560
because you were smart

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:48.760
and sent you to the Servitude Bureau,

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:50.240
thinking you'd behave.

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:52.960
But you remained reckless

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:55.000
and schemed against my consort.

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:57.360
You're truly suicidal.

00:08:57.760 --> 00:08:59.120
I deserve to die.

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.400
But Your Majesty,

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:03.040
if I were to die

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:04.560
for exposing

00:09:04.760 --> 00:09:07.080
Consort Wan's use of forbidden pills,

00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:09.800
it would shame the imperial family.

00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:11.760
So my death

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.720
must not be related to Consort Wan

00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:15.120
or those forbidden pills.

00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:16.760
I implore Your Majesty

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:18.200
to grant me

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:20.320
a novel and dignified
method of execution.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:23.800
Are you threatening me
with the imperial reputation?

00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:26.200
I dare not.

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:27.360
Kneel here

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.320
and ponder

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:29.440
a novel way to die

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.160
I've never seen before.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:32.640
Alright.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:33.696
Yes.

00:09:44.499 --> 00:09:47.160
(Imperial Study)

00:09:47.160 --> 00:09:48.000
After a whole day,

00:09:48.400 --> 00:09:49.520
have you figured out

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:51.104
a novel way to die?

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.928
Your Majesty.

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:54.560
I dare not speak.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.000
You don't fear death,

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:57.520
but you dare not speak?

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:03.960
Soldiers fight the wars
to defend our nation.

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:05.680
Ministers do their job

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:06.880
to serve the people.

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:09.560
Physicians study herbs to save lives.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:11.840
I truly admire them.

00:10:12.640 --> 00:10:14.800
Though I'm merely a lowly maid,

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:16.680
I aspire

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:17.880
to a meaningful purpose

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:19.880
and an honorable death.

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:21.984
Ling Yun,

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.640
you compare yourself to soldiers,

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:25.000
ministers

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:26.800
and physicians?

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:28.400
I've never seen

00:10:28.880 --> 00:10:30.760
someone as shameless as you.

00:10:31.560 --> 00:10:32.440
Your Majesty,

00:10:32.440 --> 00:10:33.280
I don't deserve

00:10:33.520 --> 00:10:35.120
to stand with loyal ministers

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:36.400
or virtuous physicians.

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:37.824
But Your Majesty,

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:39.160
some officials

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.400
flaunt their achievements,

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:42.440
forgetting your grace
bestowed upon them.

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:45.360
Such arrogance warrants correction.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:46.480
How dare you

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.480
meddle in state affairs?

00:10:47.648 --> 00:10:48.600
Slandering ministers

00:10:48.600 --> 00:10:49.504
is a capital offense.

00:10:49.800 --> 00:10:52.000
If my death eases your burdens,

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:54.200
then I die fulfilled.

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:56.600
Thank you

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:58.560
for devising this excellent execution.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.000
Does it count

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.600
as a novel way to die?

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:05.984
Yes, it does.

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:08.240
You made yourself sound significant.

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:10.048
How novel.

00:11:12.563 --> 00:11:14.688
(Chengxi Palace)

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.840
You've grown so incapable.

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:25.560
That maid almost took you down.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:28.840
You nearly got caught
with forbidden pills yesterday.

00:11:29.240 --> 00:11:31.240
Perhaps you've been
a consort for so long

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.400
that you've forgotten why we came here.

00:11:33.640 --> 00:11:35.000
I certainly remember

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:38.920
that we're here to secure
our family's lasting power.

00:11:39.160 --> 00:11:40.440
Lasting power?

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:41.720
If this continues,

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:44.040
you might not even remain as a consort.

00:11:44.040 --> 00:11:44.960
How dare you!

00:11:48.760 --> 00:11:51.360
Even if Ling Yun gains
His Majesty's attention,

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:52.520
she's no threat.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:55.120
Didn't our brother return triumphantly?

00:11:55.880 --> 00:11:57.440
His Majesty is hosting a banquet.

00:11:57.880 --> 00:11:58.800
Just watch.

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:01.320
I swear I'll make that wench die

00:12:01.840 --> 00:12:03.520
in the most humiliating way.

00:12:03.560 --> 00:12:05.000
Don't be so sure.

